  <summary date="2017-09-05T19:57:57Z" status="Introduced in Senate">SAFE Transitional License Act

This bill amends the S.A.F.E. Mortgage Licensing Act of 2008 to temporarily allow loan originators that meet specified requirements to continue to originate loans after moving: (1)&#160;from one state to another, or (2) from a depository institution to a non-depository institution.</summary>
